PN,36501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FA "thrill-seeking" teenager who caused
OL,8,Fthe death of his friend as he rode his
OL,9,Fe-scooter through a red light and into
OL,10,Fthe path of oncoming traffic in
OL,11,FManchester has walked free from court.
OL,13,FPassenger Jacob Calland, 14, was on
OL,14,Fthe back of the e-scooter and suffered
OL,15,F"irreversible" severe brain injuries
OL,16,Ffrom the collision in Wythenshawe, on
OL,17,F19 March 2025. He died days later in
OL,18,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe male youth - who was also 14 and
OL,8,Fcannot be named for legal reasons -
OL,9,Fsustained serious injuries including a
OL,10,Fbleed on the brain and numerous
OL,11,Ffractures.
OL,13,FHe was sentenced at Manchester Crown
OL,14,FCourt to a 18-month rehabilitation
OL,15,Forder on Tuesday 30 June after he
OL,16,Fpleaded guilty at an earlier hearing
OL,17,Fto causing death by dangerous driving.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FProsecutors said the exact speed the e-
OL,8,Fscooter was travelling at before it
OL,9,Fwas struck by a BMW on Southmoor Road
OL,10,Fat the junction of Timpson Road, could
OL,11,Fnot be determined but it was in a
OL,12,F"turbo mode" setting of up to 28mph.
OL,14,FThe boy, who is now 15, sat in court
OL,15,Fwith his father as Judge Suzanne
OL,16,FGoddard KC told him: "It is clear from
OL,17,Fdashcam footage, CCTV and eyewitness
OL,18,Fstatements that you were driving at
OL,19,Fspeed when you entered the junction
OL,20,Fand too fast for you and the driver to
OL,21,Favoid the collision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"I am satisfied your actions were
OL,8,Freckless. You were seeking the thrill
OL,9,Fof riding a scooter at high speed and
OL,10,Fnot thinking of the danger you were
OL,11,Fplacing yourself and Jacob in.
OL,13,F"The e-scooter should not have been
OL,14,Fused on a public road at all. The use
OL,15,Fof privately owned e-scooters remains
OL,16,Fillegal on public roads, cycle lanes,
OL,17,Fpavements and public parks."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FThe court heard the youth had a "very
OL,8,Funstable, traumatic upbringing",
OL,9,Frarely attended school and had not
OL,10,Ftaken a cycling proficiency course.
OL,12,FHowever, he was said to have made
OL,13,F"remarkable progress" since the crash,
OL,14,Fafter moving out of the area to live
OL,15,Fwith his father.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FJudge Goddard said it was clear from a
OL,8,Fpre-sentence report and a psychiatric
OL,9,Fassessment that the teenager was
OL,10,F"genuinely and deeply remorseful...
OL,11,Fand is struggling with his feelings of
OL,12,Fguilt for what he did".
OL,14,FShe told the court: "I consider that
OL,15,Fbecause of his age, background and
OL,16,Flack of maturity his culpability is
OL,17,Fmuch lower than otherwise would be the
OL,18,Fcase.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"Jacob was a friend and he is deeply
OL,8,Fupset at the devastation caused to
OL,9,FJacob's family.
OL,11,F"In my judgment, sending him to
OL,12,Fcustody would put him at risk of
OL,13,Fserious mental health issues, damage
OL,14,Fhis education prospects and increase
OL,15,Fhis risk of reoffending."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FDetective Constable Steve Pennington,
OL,8,Ffrom Greater Manchester Police, said:
OL,9,F"This was a tragic incident and one
OL,10,Fthat could have been avoidable. The
OL,11,Fongoing efforts of Jacob's mother
OL,12,FCarly have been truly commendable and
OL,13,Fto see her utilising her emotions and
OL,14,Fgrief to power and promote a worthy
OL,15,Fcause has been inspiring to see.
OL,17,F"E-scooters are not harmless toys and
OL,18,Fthey can lead to horrific consequences
OL,19,Fwhen used by inexperienced riders and
OL,20,Fwithout the due care required.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"I would urge parents to check what
OL,8,Ftheir children are using and to ensure
OL,9,Fthey are educated about the risks of
OL,10,Fusing them on the road."
OL,12,FThe teenager, who had no previous
OL,13,Fconvictions or cautions, was also
OL,14,Fbanned from driving for five years.
OL,16,FEarlier Jacob's mother, Carly Calland,
OL,17,Fread her victim impact statement in
OL,18,Fcourt as she said: "My heart has been
OL,19,Fsmashed into a thousand pieces and
OL,20,Fthere is nothing that can be done to
OL,21,Ffix it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1782841690
OL,3,CTeenager who caused the death of his
OL,4,Cfriend on e-scooter walks free from
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,F"Jacob's toothbrush is still in the
OL,8,Fbathroom and his favourite noodles are
OL,9,Fstill in the kitchen cupboard. The
OL,10,Fhouse is so quiet without him and I
OL,11,Fmiss him so much.
OL,13,F"The collision happened on a main road
OL,14,Fvery close to my home. I broke down in
OL,15,Ftears and had a panic attack just
OL,16,Ftrying to cross the road for the first
OL,17,Ftime after Jacob's death.
OL,19,F"I now avoid driving if I can because
OL,20,FI am petrified I could collide with an
OL,21,Fe-scooter."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
